item.description:
We discussed moving the date of the meetups to the 4th Thursday of the month. Let's start with this coming month of Feb and see how it goes...

I'd like to suggest this next meet up - everyone bring in thier favorite photo book. It can be any book with photos that you find interesting. Bring it so you can share with the group!

Also, Please bring any new work you've done over the last few months and share with us. We'd really like to see more photos from you all, so think about making a print or two and bring it along! Or feel free to bring a labtop or web address.

I'd also like to thank everyone who sent me a JPEG for the WPC web site!

We very much look forward to seeing you and again.
